<br />Yes, it's that big. It's a Sonic clone. <em>Sonic the Hedgehog</em> games can be big: <em>Sonic 2</em> was 1024 KiB, and <em>Sonic 3</em> was so big (4096 KiB) that they had to split it up over two 2048 KiB cartridges, using <em>Sonic &amp; Knuckles</em> as an expansion pak in a Game Genie-like configuration for <em>Sonic 3</em>.</div>

